wishlist.note_wishlist_refreshtips: After unlocking the Wish List, its status will reset every 2 days for the first 3 resets, after which it resets every 3 days. During the reset, if there are wishlisted heroes that have not been obtained yet, both the increased chance of summoning them and the guarantee count will be retained.
